Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, More', 'Entrectinib, Pralsetinib, Dabrafenib, Dacomitinib, Pexidartinib, Tepotinib, Fedratinib, Larotrectinib, Vemurafenib, Lapatinib, Selumetinib, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/2707/', '[1] "Product Information. Campath (alemtuzumab)" Berlex, Richmond, CA.[2] "Product Information. Lonsurf (tipiracil-trifluridine)." Taiho Oncology, Inc., Princeton, NJ.', 1767369485);
