, Bosutinib, More', 'Dextromethorphan, Valbenazine, Dalfampridine, Sodium oxybate, Riluzole, Tetrabenazine, Amifampridine, Deutetrabenazine, Tafamidis', 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/2865/', '[1] "Product Information. Tegsedi (inotersen)." Akcea Therapeutics, Cambridge, MA.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] "Product Information. Brukinsa (zanubrutinib)." BeiGene USA, Inc, San Mateo, CA.', 1767369485);
